  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a wok or skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic, chopped onion, and sliced bell peppers. Stir-fry for about 2 minutes until onions are translucent.",
    "Stir in green olives and lime juice. Cook for another minute to allow flavors to meld together.",
    "Pour the coconut milk into the wok while stirring continuously. Add bhuna spices mix and water.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer for 5 minutes until thickened slightly.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste before serving hot."
